<h2>Data Deletion</h2>
<p>All data in WeightCare is stored locally on your device. This means that uninstalling the app will automatically delete all stored data, including your weight entries and desired weight.</p>
<p>To manually delete your data without uninstalling the app:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Open the WeightCare app on your device.</li>
  <li>Go to Settings.</li>
  <li>Tap "Remove All Records".</li>
  <li>This will delete all stored weight entries and your desired weight locally.</li>
  <li>Note: This does NOT delete data used by Google Ads (AdMob), which is managed by Google.</li>
</ol>
